rComments: An amazing prof! If you actually want to learn french take a course with her. She makes it fun and interesting. She is always available to answer questions, her assignments are relatively easy, but a good determinant of how much studying you have done.  She tries to get everyone to talk in french a little during each class. Amazing Prof!

This woman is HORRIBLE. The person on 10/30/06 was absolutely right - she will find the most ridiculous reasons to deduct marks if she doesn't like you. She refuses to give any help or answer any questions. If you question her marking she just takes it out on your next assignment. If she doesn't like you, it doesn't matter how hard you work.

This professor picks favourites and is not very kind if she does not like you.  She'll deduct you marks, even if you deserve them, just because she doesn't care for you.  She is very unfair.  She will also discriminate against you if your accept isn't pure "quebecois."
